name: The Bridge Less Traveled
description:
This is a bridge that I can call home. After they put up a new highway system and a new bridge over the river, most traffic passes by this bridge and the town of Cotter.
I find myself often taking the more scenic route which involves driving over this bridge and finding a quiet place to park to give space to my overactive mind. 
Every time I look at this image I captured, it gives me a little breathing space between my thoughts.
